Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數異界體正從西南方接近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計再三十分鐘抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是群體行動的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒帶頭的就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集群防禦系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一、第二靈智型部隊在西南方島嶼迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第四、第五部隊在本島西南沿岸佈下防線
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那些來自宇宙的鼠輩見識一下人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以見識到人類軍的本事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們連所羅門系統都還不會使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.51,0:02:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旺茲是位優秀的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會這麼輕易敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會祈禱他們不要重蹈摩達維亞的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在CDC是人類軍的指揮總部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去那裡又能做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連系統都不會用的人 我怎麼能信賴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你要做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想以這種方式跟妳重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶 你要做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先待在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能夠活在世界上的某處 就是我唯一上戰場的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為我走太慢才害妳跟不上大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 不過妳不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我才剛到外面來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不太適應怎麼走路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就邊休息邊走吧 不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意聽我一個請求嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.01,0:03:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 要我揹妳都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望妳可以當我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我連一個朋友都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的朋友不就在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 小芹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有自我介紹過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是避難所的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芹就跟大家在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城不就是總士學長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說定囉 我們要當朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 - 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一波動屏障被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有變更前進路線 正筆直往這裡前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直線前進嗎 竟敢瞧不起我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已經取得外出許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思 我是為了比較虛弱的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時候人類彼此卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 妳在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情要麻煩當初把我放到系統裡面的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生至今第一次來到外界 所以我還不太會走路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳拿一個可以載我移動的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波動屏障被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校也卯足全力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說對吧 卡農
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也比平常還有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛去見我以前的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.94,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神劍型法夫那要出馬囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西南方登陸 自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昂宿型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Triple SIX 前往支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就到囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡農 帶第三部隊繞到左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夾擊它們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 連無線通訊都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Mark III！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體表面跟皮膚的觸感同步的程度居然這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好沈重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是神劍型的特徵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快和它同化並接受變性意識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳 站起來打 不然會沒命的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次這樣跟妳說話呢 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨蛇級潛水艦被擊中 三艘都被擊沈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的首領呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知另外的兩艘潛水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對西南部沿岸進行密集攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連自己人也一起打？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生以來第一次玩泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 只是表面燒掉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選擇是從現在才開始喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西方出現了第三群
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這座島的西南部份切離 用系統讓它自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把登陸的敵人和島嶼一起炸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊系統自行運作 拒絕我們的手動控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會動？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰在操縱的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法查明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.38,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃飯了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部、總部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮系統似乎被截斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情勢正有所變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓我們離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？這是誰幹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來好像是想要引導我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新建立防線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能動的傢伙通通到前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量的昂宿型異界體在龍宮山頂集結
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是島的痛楚傳到我身上而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一妳有什麼三長兩短…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我躲起來的話 這座島一定會沉沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前 我必須讓大家做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍骨區塊 (Keel Block)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兀爾德之泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是強迫要接受的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以自己的意志重新選擇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發呆了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要駕駛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎也曾經沒換裝就駕駛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在不戰鬥就對不起我爸跟甲洋他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是給予大家想要得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓大家再做一次選擇 確定所要的究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這對異界體也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要請它們做選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我才會誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴回去吧 避難所還很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳陪我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為系統的研究員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 身為島上的居民我要親眼見證一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被引導來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟王之室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第二CDC嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本構造跟CDC一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認所有系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把龍宮島的主控權拿回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是這座島 這座島就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在島上的人們想將島變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些人們的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們實際上在追求什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人們得以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有請他們做出選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.17,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓人們得以理解…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我沒能讓妳做出選擇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也選擇過囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.91,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有自我 這就是我的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前有117隻登陸 敵方勢力更加擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昂宿型會發現這裡只是時間上的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二防衛系統呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在執行中 再兩分鐘完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群體中誕生的主體將索敵系統無效化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法發現本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以拿法夫那當誘餌 引誘出敵人的首領嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很難 但我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門有反應了 是敵人首領
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將所有迎擊系統集中起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌聲的來源在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是龍宮島西邊的燈塔 我把影像顯示在螢幕上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要讓異界體選擇嗎 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人本體開始朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有法夫那散開 立刻往島的西邊移動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開敵人前往指示的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要攻擊敵人的本體！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼敵人我都會打倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕、好可怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝吧 高拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的動作…是駕駛員換人了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡農 找到敵方首領了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們往西邊移動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他還可以動的也跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底飛彈準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark V以神盾系統阻止敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VIII繞到右側
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark III確認敵方核心並且將其破壞！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊 劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准去 維持陣型！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連神劍型也抵擋不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標再度朝燈塔移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城乙姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你們也選好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有對話的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都會消失的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛無的道路…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做選擇的並不是只有你們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 我們逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 會被炸掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的核心正從內部被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒被同化了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標又開始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所羅門的反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要尋找就找得到喔 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振動、各種波形、溫度、電子、電波、空間相位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體攻擊之後所留下來的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員 你聽得到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的位置捕捉到了 幫忙打倒那傢伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要跟系統同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能跟Mark XI那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你曾經說過只有這座島是唯一的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初我不懂這句話的含意 也不知道你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽你的話去戰鬥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我覺得有點懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們一無所知的時候 你就想要保護這座島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是翔子還有甲洋那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也獨自背負著痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體的識別代號是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Zein
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟系統同步必須登錄機體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我五秒鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登錄完畢 開始同步處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見我看到的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個武器是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是Mark VIII的44機關砲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怕的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路迦之槍嗎！
